          "lines": [
            {
              "speaker": "Yusuf",
              "text": "I've agreed to let you use the bank. What do you want today?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "This is an odd-looking bank."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Yusuf",
              "text": "It's an odd-looking town. Those Corsairs are basically no better than pirates, you know, and the adventurers they bring in are worse. That's why I keep a cannon for protection."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Yusuf",
              "text": "Anyway, did you want something?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I want nothing."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Yusuf",
              "text": "Then you shall get it."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
